	<blockcenter>
		<title>Visualização de Mídias em Galerias</title>
		<body>
			<p>O XMLNuke permite listar as suas mídias, sejam elas Fotos, Vídeos, Youtube, QuickTime, etc, utilizando o conjunto de XML nele existente</p>
			<p>
				<code information="Código XML da Galeria de Mídias (Album de Fotografia, Flash, etc)"><![CDATA[
<mediagallery name="testing">
  <mediaitem src="" thumb="" caption="" title="" width="" height="" />
</mediagallery>
]]></code>

			</p>
			
				
			<p>Album de Fotos
			<mediagallery name="testing">
				<mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/1.jpg" thumb="common/imgs/albumsample/t_1.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Image 1" width="60" height="60" />
				<mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/2.jpg" thumb="common/imgs/albumsample/t_2.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Image 2" width="60" height="60" />
				<mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/3.jpg" thumb="common/imgs/albumsample/t_3.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Image 3" width="60" height="60" />
				<mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/4.jpg" thumb="common/imgs/albumsample/t_4.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Image 4" width="60" height="60" />
				<mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/5.jpg" thumb="common/imgs/albumsample/t_5.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Image 5" width="60" height="60" />
			</mediagallery>
			</p>

			<p>Flash
			<mediagallery name="flash">
				<mediaitem src="http://www.adobe.com/products/flashplayer/include/marquee/design.swf?width=792&amp;height=294" thumb="http://images.apple.com/trailers/wb/images/terminatorsalvation_200903131052.jpg" caption="This is a Flash Source" title="Flash Source"/>
			</mediagallery>
			</p>

			<p>Quicktime Movie
			<mediagallery name="mov">
				<mediaitem src="http://movies.apple.com/movies/wb/terminatorsalvation/terminatorsalvation-tlr3_h.480.mov?width=480&amp;height=204" thumb="http://images.apple.com/trailers/wb/images/terminatorsalvation_200903131052.jpg" caption="This is a Quicktime movie" title="Quicktime Movie"/>
			</mediagallery>
			</p>

			<p>Youtube Video
			<mediagallery name="youtube">
				<mediaitem src="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4m48GqaOz90" thumb="http://i1.ytimg.com/vi/4m48GqaOz90/default.jpg" caption="This is from Youtube" title="Youtube clip"/>
			</mediagallery>
			</p>

			<p>Iframe
			<mediagallery name="iframe">
				<mediaitem src="engine:xmlnuke?xml=home&amp;xsl=preview&amp;iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=300" caption="This is a IFrame" title="View IFRAME"/>
			</mediagallery>
			</p>
			<p>
			Isolado: <mediaitem src="common/imgs/albumsample/6.jpg" caption="You can add a caption to this photo" title="Clique aqui" width="60" height="60" /></p>
